Big Brother Naija 2019 ex-housemate, Cindy Okafor took to Instagram to show off a car gift she got from a friend. Posing in her new car, Cindy said her friend that sent it over told her “she deserves the best” and should also continue being herself. She wrote; And she said: @florichceo : You deserve the best and you shall have it, just keep being you. me: CAPITAL LETTER “THANK YOU”